Title: Editing view elements with single info context was loosing them during saving
Level: 1
Edition: cee
Component: reporting
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
State: unknown
Version: 1.2.7i1
Date: 1423231419

When editing a report element of type service which has a single object context, for
example is related to a single host, just loading and saving the element resulted
in the view loosing the single object context.
